# Epal Shop — bridge.map
#
# What this company rolls UP to the Group through the kernel event bridge.
# Format:  <domain.event>  ->  <group.bucket>   (target account code)
# DECLARATIVE ONLY until Phase 3 wires the bridge; account codes are the TARGET
# mapping and must be reconciled with the ledger chart-of-accounts before the
# old on-read consolidation path is removed (numbers must match exactly).
#
pos.sale             -> group.revenue    (4001)
purchase.recorded    -> group.expense    (5002)
stock.adjusted       -> group.inventory  (1200)
expense.recorded     -> group.expense    (5001)
